Package: geotidy
Title: Tidy manipulation of spatial data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Etienne",
           family = "Racine",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "etiennebr@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1109-894X"))
Description: Manipulate spatial data tidily. `Geotidy` provides a selection of 
    spatial functions from the `sf` package that are adapted to a tidy workflow. 
    It relies on tibbles and `dplyr` verbs, and forces you to be explicit about 
    the spatial operations you desire. 
